                        <text>
                            <div>
                                <p>A code to indicate the type of consent.</p>
                                <p>The Coded with Code System datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>The <em>code </em>attribute will contain a value from the list of codes in the <u>DemographicConsentObservationType</u> vocabulary</li>
                                </ul>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>The <em>codeSystem </em>attribute will contain the OID "2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.17.164"</li>
