                                    <p>The value of the consent status.</p>
                                    <p> The Coded with Code System datatype flavour is used to carry this information as follows:</p>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>The <em>code </em>attribute will contain a value from the list of codes in the Consent vocabulary</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>The <em>codeSystem </em>attribute will contain the OID "2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.16.2"</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </text>
